instructions: put the plate on top of the charger in the center of the charger.
put the napkin in the center of the plate in the vertical position
Put the dinner fork on the left side of the charger, the progs facing up
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with the progs in line with the dinner fork
put the dinner knife on the right of the charger with the blade facing the charger
put the tea spoon to the right of the knife with the bowl facing the vertical position
put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon with the bowl in the vertical position
put the water glass above the knife, but in between the charger and the knife
put the wine glass to the right of the water glass and above the tea spoon
put the wine glass below the other wine glass and above the tea spoon
put the coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon, but in line with the inner wine glass
put the bread plate above the forks with the center of the plate in line with the wine glass
put the butter knife horizontally on top of the bread plate with the blade facing to the right
put the dessert fork horizontally above the plate with the prongs facing to the right
put the dessert spoon horizontally above the plate with the bowl facing the left of the plate
